<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(22, 24, 22, 0.08);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f5e800, #7eed5e);
            padding: 4px 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
            color: #161816;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #161816;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #3F634D;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            border-left: 4px solid #7eed5e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f5e800, #7eed5e);
            color: #161816 !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(126, 237, 94, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(245, 232, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f5e800, #7eed5e);
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #161816;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #f4f7f6;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #7eed5e;
        }
        .signature p {
            color: #161816;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header"></div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Dear candidate,</p>
            
            <p class="message">
                Thank you for your interest in working with <strong>Brandafrik</strong>.
            </p>

            <p class="message">
                To proceed with your application, please complete the short assessment linked below:
            </p>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{invitationLink}}" class="cta-button">Take Assessment</a>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #3F634D; font-size: 15px;">
                    This helps us better understand your skills and suitability for the role.
                </p>
            </div>

            {{#if deadline}}
            <p class="message">
                Kindly complete the assessment by <strong style="color: #161816;">{{deadline}}</strong>.
            </p>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p class="message">
                If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email. We look forward to reviewing your submission!
            </p>

            <div class="signature">
                <p style="margin: 0;">Warm Regards,</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0;"><strong>The Brandafrik team.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0;">
                &copy; {{year}} Brandafrik. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
